{
  "stem": "833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, he came to-- I said, listen, if he dies here-- and he might-- he might die here, in the next two days-- then I make you responsible.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then you are-- Or, better still, [LAUGHS] Austrian-- it was just funny-- I mean, it was my last act of-- of Austrian superiority.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they let him go-- let him go-- or, no, they put him to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They found out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the way he got free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't want to talk about that again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was most beastly, most terrifying, most ugly, most inhuman, most ghastly experience of my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ride itself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those 13 hours from Vienna to Dachau were the worst thing that I can experience.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there were learned-- Again, I said, after some hours I began to learn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When the shock-- the shock went off, I start to learn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I learned how beastly people can be made-- to what extent they can be manipulated to become worse than animals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I shouldn't even say as animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Animals are probably very kind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were then Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were manipulated the same way I explained to you-- by-- by the hatred, by-- by-- the obvious thing, you see, Hitler was very clever, in one way, to have the obvious as the thing itself it means.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there were Jewish bankers, Jewish people who owned department stores.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To tell them that's the way they rob the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then obvious things to tell them-- that all their ills, all their difficulties, all their problems-- this was this-- what I call the middle-- middle slime of people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, who were half-educated-- or, let's say, a third educated, who didn't know-- really had not the ability to think.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
